HEADWORD: Baroness
<hw>Bar"on*ess</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A baron's wife;
also, a lady who holds the baronial title in her own right; <as>as, the
<ex>Baroness</ex> Burdett-Coutts</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
